               <id root="26013282-48e6-583c-e054-00144ff8d46c"/>
               <code code="34066-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="BOXED WARNING SECTION"/>
               <title>Boxed Warning</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph> fetal toxicity</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>When pregnancy is detected, discontinue losartan potassium tablets as soon as possible.
  <br/>
Drugs that act directly on the rennin-angiotensin system can cause injury and death to the developing fetus. See WARNINGS, Fetal Toxicity.
 </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20151203"/>
            </section>
